    <td style="width:10%">Parameterization
    <td>`T` is [SIGNEDINTEGRAL]
  <tr>
    <td>Description
    <td>Reads bits from an integer, with sign extension.

    When `T` is a scalar type, then:
    <ul>
    <li>`w` is the bit width of `T`
